{"type": "article", "id": 8860, "title": "Flyte 磁悬浮灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-24T07:27:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235203XIZOifxq3BalR7KT.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t有人为了让灯具变得酷炫，添加了许多精巧的设计和装饰，Simon Morris 则痴迷技术的力量，一个普通的灯泡，可忽然“悬浮”起来，一切就变得不一样了。这款叫做 “Flyte” 的电灯采用磁悬浮技术通过空气进行无线供电。其底座采用的是橡木、白蜡木与桃木的结合，看上去简单优雅。而除了供电，“Flyte” 还可以为手机无线充电。目前产品售价 199 美元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，可以<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flyte/flyte-levitating-light\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352019lAISMYguqeDjW8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.94558824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235201rBTmCqYIJ65kzlDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.15441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235202ikahL6EeUmgyYZtc.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}